Some knowledge for you guys.
Symbiosis: 2 different organisms living together.
Mutualism: Both organisms benefit.
Commensalism: One benefits the other could care less.
Parasitism: One organism benefits the other may be weakened.

So when Rhett said that the that wasn't very symbiotic he was pretty much 
saying that it wasn't 2 different organisms living together.﻿
